data.description: *$10,000 Towards Interest Rate Buydown with Acceptable Offer!  Impressive Newer Built 5 Bedroom Home on a Quiet Street! Open Concept Kitchen, Living Room, & Formal Dining on Main level with Laminated Hardwood Floors. Large Kitchen with plenty of Cabinets, Counter Space, Pantry, Center Island and Morning Room with Tons of Natural Light. Office/Den on main level with French Doors; Master Bedroom with tray ceiling and large walk in closet; Master Bathroom with Dual Sinks and Oversized Walk In Shower; 4 Additional Nice Sized Bedrooms and Loft Area; Great Location - Close to Interstate, Schools, and Shopping! Clark Pleasant School System - Don't let this Opportunity Pass You By!
